Package Food

Class Meal

  • java.lang.Object
    • Food.Meal

  • public class Meal
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles construction of and exported method for Meal ADT. Effectively acts as wrapper for cleanly handling an ArrayList of Foods and common methods that will need to be applied to such a selection.
    Author:
    Wyatt Wismer
